<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="enough-pron">enough <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪ'nʌf/    美 /ɪ'nʌf/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>足够；充分：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Enough is as good as a feast. 
凡事适可而止。/知足常乐。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We have <strong>enough to do</strong> to finish the job on time. 
要按时完成这项工作，我们还得加倍努力。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="have-had-enough-of">have had enough (of)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[口语] 够了 / 受够了：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have had enough of your rudeness. 
我受够了你的无礼！</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Although she did not know Boston well, she made her way <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (足够容易) to the Home Circle
Building.  （2006 湖南改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. easily enough  </p></div>